{"title":"秋日特辑 | 去川西，去最接近天堂的地方","uid":"74544a5b5216c424c5b8f8e62fd899f7","slug":"推文13","date":"2021-11-07T16:00:00.000Z","updated":"2022-03-03T16:08:24.072Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/推文13.json","keywords":null,"cover":"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304000524351.png","content":"<p><strong>横断山脉</strong></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304000407805.png\" alt=\"image-20220304000407805\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304000447455.png\" alt=\"image-20220304000447455\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304000452060.png\" alt=\"image-20220304000452060\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"阿坝：童话世界\"><a href=\"#阿坝：童话世界\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"阿坝：童话世界\"></a>阿坝：童话世界</h2><p>为“世界生态旅游最佳目的地”的阿坝州平日里，我们在成都遥望四姑娘山。</p>\n<p>这次，我们翻过巴朗山，越过垭口亲自站在了她的脚下。在猫鼻梁伫足望去，四座并排的山峰就像四位头戴纱巾的姑娘：</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304000507842.png\" alt=\"image-20220304000507842\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304000512606.png\" alt=\"image-20220304000512606\"></p>\n<p>四姑娘山景区由双桥沟、长坪沟、海子沟组成<br>其中以双桥沟的景色最为迷人</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304000520203.png\" alt=\"image-20220304000520203\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304000524351.png\" alt=\"image-20220304000524351\"></p>\n<p>白塔与彩林</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304000533266.png\" alt=\"image-20220304000533266\"></p>\n<p>四姑娘山的另一面即是观赏彩林的绝佳胜地毕棚沟<br>每到十月毕棚沟的彩林从谷底绵延到山巅在阳光的照耀下显得光彩熠熠</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304000537482.png\" alt=\"image-20220304000537482\"></p>\n","text":"横断山脉 阿坝：童话世界为“世界生态旅游最佳目的地”的阿坝州平日里，我们在成都遥望四姑娘山。 这次，我们翻过巴朗山，越过垭口亲自站在了她的脚下。在猫鼻梁伫足望去，四座并排的山峰就像四位头戴纱